192
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:30,960
 Evo kad se to spojilo, ja sam odjednom krenuo sjećaj da meni to paše.

193
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:34,720
 I nisam znao ni to izjasni, nisam znao ni šta je,

194
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:40,660
